channel.description:
[center][img]http://i33.tinypic.com/9apxy1.png[/img][/center] [center][img]http://i36.tinypic.com/aot0g8.png[/img][/center] [center][b][size=10pt]iFactored is a bunch of programmers with knowledge of c++,Java,HTML,Python,Batch the programmers are working on a special project which will involve lots of hard work bringing back old runescape but better we will add tons of npc's, fix tons of glitches, add great pking and adding adventure so people can have there old memories,also this project will be fun work and also quite long so please be patient don't flame us.[/size][/b][/center] [center][img]http://i37.tinypic.com/1195n53.png[/img][/center]
- Barrows with kill-count [b]100%[/b] - Duel arena pretty much [b]100%[/b] - Trading [b]100% [/b] - Specials All specs are [b]100% [/b] - Throwing knifes [b]100%[/b] - Range [b]85%[/b] - Npc magic [b]100%[/b] - Alch (low/high) and telegrab [b]100%[/b] - basic banning and anti flood system [b]100%[/b] - 2handed weapons + shield fix [b]100%[/b] - Pvp | Mage | Melee | range - Crystal bow degrading improved to support multiple bows - Basic following - Attack option when in wildy and remove when out of wild. - Teleblock works and you can't teleport above level 20 wild - Npc combat (hit delays, npc dieing emotes, re-spawn time) - Ranging (bow with arrow requirements, dropping arrows, arrows fired from x and y even when running) - Normal and Ancient magic (freezing works, healing blood spell work) - Npc Drops (very simple to add new npc) - Eating food - Picking up items - Dieing - Burying bones - Prayer [b]100%[/b] [center] [center] [img]http://i38.tinypic.com/ndq5on.png[/img][/center]
